Veven left immediately after you began fighting,
saying he did not need to watch to know the outcome.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev051513_MSG0002
rows.name:
I expect he just did not want to see his beloved
machine lose.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev051513_MSG0003
rows.name:
I will see to repairing it, then cart it back to Biahno
Lake at once.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev051513_MSG0004
rows.name:

rows.label: qev051513_MSG0005
rows.name: For now, I thank you for the precious data.[ST:wait ]
